# Expensify Reviews
## Read Customer Service Reviews of www.expensify.com
Expensify has a rating of 4.7 out of 5 stars based on 867 reviews.

### Summary
Reviewers overwhelmingly had a great experience with Expensify. Customers consistently praise the platform's user-friendliness, highlighting its simple and intuitive design. People appreciate how easy it is to navigate, submit, and manage expenses, saving them significant time and effort.

### Review Summary
* Reviewers praise the platform's user-friendliness and simplicity
* The mobile app is particularly well-received for its convenience and ease of use
* Consumers value the platform's efficiency and automation features, such as SmartScan technology
* The seamless integration with other apps and the ability to generate automated reports are also highly appreciated

